testtool

Class TestTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • testtool.TestTool

  • public class TestTool
extends java.lang.Object
    Top-level model class for the TestTool program. TestTool has references to each of the functional model components of the tool. There is also a reference to the TestToolDB class for interacting with the database.
